Payroll cancellation is a critical process to ensure proper handling of employer requests. There are two main types of payroll cancellations:
1Ô∏è‚É£ Same-Day Payroll Cancellation ‚Äì The payroll is already in processing.
2Ô∏è‚É£ Future-Dated Payroll Cancellation ‚Äì The payroll is scheduled for a future date and hasn‚Äôt started processing.

This document outlines:
‚úÖ How cancellation requests are received and processed.
‚úÖ How ACH, SafePay, and EventBridge are impacted.
‚úÖ Decision points for in-flight cancellations vs. waiting until processing completes.

